  <name>xanadOS Search &amp; Destroy</name>
  <summary>Comprehensive Linux security scanner and system protection suite</summary>
  
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>GPL-3.0-or-later</project_license>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      xanadOS Search &amp; Destroy is a powerful and user-friendly security scanner 
      that brings enterprise-grade malware detection to Linux desktop users and 
      system administrators.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>ClamAV virus and malware scanning with modern PyQt6 GUI</li>
      <li>Real-time file system monitoring and protection</li>
      <li>RKHunter rootkit detection integration</li>
      <li>YARA heuristic malware detection engine</li>
      <li>Hybrid multi-engine scanning (ClamAV + YARA)</li>
      <li>Smart scan result caching (70-80% faster rescans)</li>
      <li>Adaptive worker thread scaling for optimal performance</li>
      <li>System load-aware scanning with automatic throttling</li>
      <li>Comprehensive performance metrics and reporting</li>
      <li>Scheduled security scans</li>
      <li>Quarantine management for detected threats</li>
      <li>Multiple scan modes: Quick, Full, and Custom</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Designed for ease of use while providing powerful features for advanced users.
      Perfect for protecting your desktop, laptop, or server from malware and security threats.
    </p>
  </description>
  
